{
  "stem": "304.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after three weeks they-- they lost the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember two days and two nights how the people from the Polish army-- soldiers and officers on bicycles and on horseback and in wagons-- they went through our city.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were standing out there looking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was watching.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was interesting, because as a little town and so much commotion.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I really didn't understand the seriousness of the situation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I just watched, because so many people were marching on-- on the streets.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then, later, we started to hear what was going on in Poland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "What really happened-- this was '39.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In '41, yeah, then we were occupied by the Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "After the-- the-- the Polish left and one day we were occupied by the Hungarians and then our lives changed very, very dramatically and drastically at once.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because under the Hungarians, we were still at home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But, we had million restrictions.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "First, I will tell you is what affected me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was first year junior high school when the Hungarians came in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then I was the last one that I was allowed to finish the three years of junior high school.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "All the children were younger than I, one year or more, couldn't attend any more public school.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So the parents had to make a private schools and so they could go on with their studies.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Then, when I finished junior high school, I wanted very badly to go to gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And were a very famous, huge gymnasium with all the kids from the neighbor villages used to come there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "My mother took me-- I had a beautiful report card, one of the best-- and took me to the principal.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And looked at it and he said, oh what a beautiful report card.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
